  # About
  I'm Jacky. I live in [Brooklyn, New York][bk] and from République d'Haïti,
  although I was born on American soil. I spend too much time in front of my
  [laptop][laptop] when I'm either at home or at a space where I can use it
  (which tends to be almost anywhere). I'm an unapologetically Black cisgender
  male and if the concepts of equal rights for Blacks is trippy, you've just
  made a `403`, pal.

