  ## Programming
  My dad gave me a book on C++ programming back in 2006. I read it over that
  summer and kept tinkering with little text games on a Windows XP machine.
  From there, I learned about [Ubuntu][ubuntu] in 2009 and kept using it since
  then. Check out my [Github][github] account.

  ## Photography
  Oh God. So when I said I took pictures, I meant it. But they tend to not
  have people in them. They're kind of hard to take pictures of. I'm working on
  it though. I put my pictures where most photographers tend to, on
  [Flickr][flickr]. Don't laugh.

  ## This Site
